profile:
*As a precautionary measure, I'm wearing a face mask at all times while working.

Young Professional with over 5 years of Painting experience.

Specializing in drywall application and a range of finishing techniques.

I provide clean, timely service at a fair price.

My Hourly rate is $35/hr. 

Your free estimate requires a home visit, and is available upon request.

The order in which I complete a basic re-paint job is as follows:

1. Sanding/plaster repair and cleanup
2. Caulking of cracks
3. Painting of trim.
4. Painting of Ceiling.
5. Taping of trim.
6. Cutting in and Painting walls. 

This process may be adjusted to suite client preference/budget upon request.

*now offering a 10% discount upon completion of a Homestars review.
